<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>9 Essential Elements of a High-Converting Thank You Page (+ Examples)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Thank You Pages [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-91260" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Thank-You-Pages-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e999ff47a592" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There’s a page on your site that’s a goldmine waiting to be tapped. It’s not your </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-product-pages"><span style="font-weight: 400;">product page</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Nor is it your </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization"><span style="font-weight: 400;">checkout page</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">…</span></p>
</div>






<p>It’s your <em>thank you </em>page.</p>



<p>Get this page right and it becomes an invisible selling machine for your online store. But get it wrong, and you risk getting your relationship with new subscribers off to a rocky start.</p>



<p>The problem, though, is <strong>many business owners massively underutilize their thank you page.&nbsp;</strong></p>



<p>They don’t ask prospects to take action—when they’re most primed to do so—and thus, forgo countless opportunities to increase revenue. Worse, most aren’t even aware they’re doing it.</p>



<p>Well, that changes right now.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>In this article, I’ll walk you through the psychology behind why thank you page converts well (hint: it’s not what you think). I’ll also show you how to get more mileage out of your thank you page by following nine best practices today’s pros are using.</p>



<p>Let’s get started.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e99a0547a593" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
