<h2><strong>9 Thank You Page Best Practices You Need to Know</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Ask for Referrals</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Ask for Social Shares</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Demonstrate Authority</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Offer a Discount</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Qualify and Nurture Leads</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Link to Your Most Popular Content</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Upsell a Product or Service</a></p>



<p><a href="#8">8. Encourage Engagement</a></p>



<p><a href="#9">9. Conduct a Survey</a></p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2><strong>The Power of Little Commitments (Or Why Thank You Pages Work)</strong></h2>



<p>As you’re probably already aware, a thank you page is a page you redirect visitors to after they opt in for a bonus on your site (or in other cases, such as e-commerce, making a purchase).&nbsp;</p>



<p>Often, its purpose is to give visitors a link to the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/evergreen-lead-magnet" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">lead magnet</a> they opted in for and to, well, thank them for signing up.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="820" height="185" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25.png" alt="Thank You For Subscribing" class="wp-image-91204" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25.png 820w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-768x173.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-600x135.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-760x171.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-155x35.png 155w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-222x50.png 222w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-740x167.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image11-25-385x87.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px" /></figure></div>



<p>While there’s nothing inherently wrong with a page like the above, it ignores an important principle in consumer psychology:</p>



<p><em>People tend to behave in ways that are consistent with an earlier action.</em></p>



<p>In other words, <strong>when someone complies with a little request—like opting in for a newsletter—they’re more likely to comply with a similar or </strong><strong><em>larger</em></strong><strong> request later (like placing an order).</strong></p>



<p>This is known as <em><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/commitment-and-consistency-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">commitment and consistency</a></em> and it’s one of the most powerful persuasion triggers in marketing.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/17217362_Compliance_Without_Pressure_The_Foot-in-the-Door_Technique" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">In one study</a> led by Jonathan Freedman and Scott Fraser, a researcher posing as a volunteer worker asked a selection of California homeowners to accept and display a little three-inch-square sign that read, “Be a safe driver.”&nbsp;</p>



<p>An easy request, right? The homeowners thought so, too: nearly all of them agreed to it.</p>



<p>But here’s where it gets interesting…</p>



<p>Two weeks later, a different volunteer worker followed up with the homeowners and asked them to allow an obstructive public-service billboard with poor lettering to be allowed on their front lawns.</p>



<p>The result?</p>



<p><em>Seventy-six percent offered the use of their front yards.</em>&nbsp;</p>



<p>As Cialdini writes in his groundbreaking book, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Influence-Psychology-Persuasion-Robert-Cialdini/dp/006124189X/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><em>Influence</em></a>,</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-style-large"><p><span class="has-inline-color has-plum-color">If I can get you to make a commitment, I will have set for your automatic and ill-considered consistency with that earlier commitment. Once a stand is taken, there is a natural tendency to behave in ways that are stubbornly consistent with the stand.&nbsp;</span></p></blockquote>



<p><a href="http://www.snacknation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">SnackNation</a>, a healthy office snack delivery service, is a perfect illustration of building commitment and consistency into their marketing.</p>



<p>When you opt in for one of their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/content-upgrades" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">content upgrades</a>, you’re redirected to this thank you page:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-1024x575.png" alt="SnackNation Form" class="wp-image-91164" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image2-26.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>On it, they give you a chance to claim a free Snack Box in exchange for a brief call with a sales rep. (The purpose of the call is to see if SnackNation is a good fit for your office.)</p>



<p>According to <a href="https://growandconvert.com/conversion-rate-optimization/thank-you-lead-generating-machine/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">their content marketing manager</a>, Emil Shour, Snacknation has not only achieved a <strong>10.52% conversion rate</strong> by doing this&#8230;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="648" height="195" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26.png" alt="Conversion Rate" class="wp-image-91172" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26.png 648w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-300x90.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-380x114.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-600x181.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-116x35.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-166x50.png 166w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-220x66.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image4-26-385x116.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;they captured <strong>884 subscribers</strong>, from which <strong>20 converted into customers.</strong>&nbsp;</p>



<p>At $249 per month that’s an additional $4,980 per month with minimal effort.</p>



<p>Not bad, huh?</p>



<p>Now that you’ve seen the earning potential of a well-optimized thank you page, let’s discuss nine thank you page strategies to try.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Ask for Referrals</strong></h2>



<p>Generating new business is an on-going challenge for many online stores.</p>



<p>But there’s one acquisition channel that, when consistent, is a predictable source of revenue:</p>



<p><em>Referrals.</em></p>



<p>In fact, according to <a href="http://www.ogilvy.com/News/Press-Releases/June-2014-Consumer-behavior-comes-under-the-spotlight-in-new-study.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">a recent survey by Ogilvy</a>, <strong>74% of consumers identify word-of-mouth as a key influencer in their purchasing decision.</strong></p>



<p>It’s no surprise, then, that many businesses ask you to refer a friend or family member when you sign up.</p>



<p>Take <a href="http://jamesclear.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">James Clear</a> for example. With over 700,000 monthly readers and more than 350,000 email subscribers, James’s blog has gone from a blank WordPress installation to one of the most popular single-author blogs in the world in less than three years.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="679" height="180" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26.png" alt="Footnotes" class="wp-image-91180" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26.png 679w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-380x101.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-600x159.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-132x35.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-189x50.png 189w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-220x58.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image5-26-385x102.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px" /></figure></div>



<p>One of the ways that he’s been able to achieve that growth is by <strong>asking for referrals on his thank you page.</strong></p>



<p>After joining his weekly newsletter, James redirects you to a page where he asks you to refer his work to a friend:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="580" height="220" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22.png" alt="Tell A Friend" class="wp-image-91184" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22.png 580w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-300x114.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-380x144.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-92x35.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-132x50.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-220x83.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image6-22-385x146.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px" /></figure></div>



<p>What’s more, he makes it <em>super</em> <em>simple</em> to do by including a pre-written email:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="205" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8.png" alt="Pre-written Email" class="wp-image-91244" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-380x130.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-146x50.png 146w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image21-8-385x132.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<p>All you have to do is click the link and press “Send” and James increases his likelihood of acquiring a new reader (and perhaps one day, a customer).</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong>&nbsp;Ask new readers to refer you to a friend using a pre-written email.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Ask for Social Shares</strong></h2>



<p>The requests you ask of your audience varies depending on factors such as demographics and psychographics.</p>



<p>(Teenagers, for example, are more likely to share something on social media than send an email referring a service like we saw in the previous example.)</p>



<p>Put another way, if you know most of your reader’s time is spent on Facebook, then asking them to ‘Like’ your page is easier than asking for a referral.</p>



<p>Let’s imagine for a moment that your goal isn’t to grow a following on social media but to push more targeted traffic through your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">marketing funnel</a>.</p>



<p>How could you encourage more social shares?</p>



<p>One option would be to leverage your <em>readers’</em> following.</p>



<p>Some influencers, like Brennan Dunn from <a href="https://doubleyourfreelancing.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Double Your Freelancing</a>, ask new email signups to share his popular email course:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="425" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-1024x425.png" alt="Popular Email Source" class="wp-image-91212" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-1024x425.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-300x124.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-768x319.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-380x158.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-600x249.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-760x315.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-84x35.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-121x50.png 121w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-740x307.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-220x91.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22-385x160.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image13-22.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Others, like Michael Hyatt, <em>incentivize</em> the share by offering a chance to win a prize:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="665" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-1024x665.png" alt="Share And Win" class="wp-image-91216" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-1024x665.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-300x195.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-768x498.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-400x260.png 400w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-380x247.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-600x389.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-760x493.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-54x35.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-77x50.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-740x480.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-220x143.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21-385x250.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image14-21.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>To learn more about how to ask for referrals on your thank you page, check out <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.smartbribe.com/" target="_blank">Smart Bribe from Growth Tools</a>.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Ask new readers to share an important page on their favorite social media channel. (Pro tip: give a reason <em>why</em> you’re asking for the share.)</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Demonstrate Authority&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Earlier in the post, we talked about the power of commitment and consistency: our tendency to be consistent with actions we’ve already taken.</p>



<p>But there’s another best practice that amplifies these principles further:</p>



<p><em>The principle of demonstrating authority.</em></p>



<p>Many businesses choose to position themselves as the go-to leader in their marketplace for this very reason: when you’re a recognized expert in your field, you don’t need to prospect for new business—customers comes to you.</p>



<p>It’s important to remember, though, that authority isn’t demonstrated by what you say about yourself or your company. Rather, it’s demonstrated by what <em>other</em> authorities say about you.</p>



<p>“As featured in” sections on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-homepage-best-practices" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">homepages</a> are a good example of this.</p>



<p>Here’s an example from Ramit Sethi from <a href="http://iwillteachyoutoberich.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">I Will Teach You to Be Rich</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-1024x575.png" alt="Footer With Clients" class="wp-image-91196" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image9-26.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This prompts something to the effect of:</p>



<p>“Wow, if he’s been featured in ABC News, CNN and The Wall Street Journal, he must be an expert!”</p>



<p>Often, you’ll notice influencers using media mentions on their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-landing-page" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">landing pages</a> and even their checkout pages.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But the savviest business owners include them <em>throughout</em> their marketing.</p>



<p>Take <a href="https://goinfinitus.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Scott Oldford</a>, for instance.</p>



<p>He demonstrates authority on his landing page, optin page, <em>and</em> thank you page.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="395" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-1024x395.png" alt="Header With Known Customers" class="wp-image-91208" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-1024x395.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-300x116.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-768x296.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-380x147.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-600x232.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-760x293.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-740x286.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-220x85.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25-385x149.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image12-25.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Knowing that the Internet marketing industry is plagued with charlatans claiming to be experts, Oldford differentiates himself by “borrowing” authority from the major media outlets that have featured him.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Trust isn’t built once, remember—it’s built gradually over time as the buyer moves through each stage of <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank">the buyer’s journey</a>. So, keep that in mind when you’re positioning yourself as an expert in your field.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Include media mentions, reviews and <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank">testimonials</a> on your thank you page <em>as well as</em> other important pages on your site.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Offer a Discount&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Having a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">discount strategy</a> is an integral part of many e-commerce businesses.</p>



<p>But it’s important to know <em>when</em> to offer them.</p>



<p>Do it often enough and your customers come to expect it. Do it sparingly and your customers can jump to a competitor.</p>



<p>Luckily, there’s a silver lining: using discounts to reward good behavior.</p>



<p><a href="https://naturebox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Naturebox</a> illustrates this strategy perfectly.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-1024x575.png" alt="Nature Box" class="wp-image-91224" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image16-21.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you choose to subscribe, you’re rewarded with a free sample of one of their bestselling items. (Note the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">scarcity</a> at the bottom to increase the likelihood the reader will claim their free gift):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="377" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-1024x377.png" alt="Get Free Bag" class="wp-image-91168" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-1024x377.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-300x111.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-768x283.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-380x140.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-600x221.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-760x280.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-95x35.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-136x50.png 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-740x273.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-220x81.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25-385x142.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image3-25.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The real magic, though, is the secondary benefit:</p>



<p>“+25% off your first order.”</p>



<p>Offering a secondary benefit doesn’t just reward <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-loyalty-programs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">customer loyalty</a>; it also <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/reduce-churn" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">reduces churn</a>.</p>



<p>Use it wisely.</p>


<div id="editors-note-block_5f771fa76bcfb" class="block-editors-note">
