<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Qualify and Nurture Leads&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Not all readers are created equally.</p>



<p>At any time, a reader is at different stages of the buyer’s journey.</p>



<p>Some are only beginning to become <em>aware</em> they have a problem. Some have defined their problem and are <em>evaluating</em> a viable solution. While others have <em>decided</em> on a solution and are ready to buy.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The question is, how do you cater to all types of readers?</p>



<p><em>You offer different choices for different readers.</em></p>



<p>Take marketing giant <a href="https://hubspotpro.dk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">HubSpot</a>, for example.</p>



<p>When you opt in, you’re given a choice on what to do next based on where you are in the buyer’s journey. If you’re only at the beginning of your journey and want to learn more about your problem, you can read a free resource on the subject:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="492" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-1024x492.png" alt="HubSpot Free Resource" class="wp-image-91236" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-1024x492.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-768x369.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-760x365.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image19-17.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But if you’re further along in your journey and are considering making a purchase, you can take a free assessment:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-1024x575.png" alt="Free Assessment" class="wp-image-91228" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image17-22.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Give people a choice and they’ll know which path is right for them.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Nudge subscribers along the buyer’s journey by offering different content types at different funnel stages (e.g. a webinar, free trial, etc.).</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Link to Your Most Popular Content&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Let’s stop for a moment and consider an important truth:</p>



<p>If a reader opts in on your site, it’s because either they got value from your content (i.e. it solved a problem for them), and/or, they believe you will continue to deliver value in the future.&nbsp;</p>



<p>With that in mind, it’s important that you meet that expectation and help prospects on their journey to purchasing from you to the best of your ability.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pat Flynn, from <a href="https://www.smartpassiveincome.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Smart Passive Income</a>, understands his audience better than most marketers. After opting in for his newsletter, Pat offers a series of eBooks solving a variety of popular pain points his audience has:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-1024x575.png" alt="Guides Created Just For You" class="wp-image-91232" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image18-19.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.groovehq.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Groove</a>, on the other hand, link to their most popular content based on social shares and comments:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-1024x575.png" alt="Thanks For Signing Up" class="wp-image-91192" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image8-27.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Linking to their most popular content, not only benefits the reader, but it also benefits the blog.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The more eyes on their content, the higher the link-building opportunity and the better their content will rank in the search engine results pages (SERPs).</p>



<p>Win. Win.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Link any content you want to rank well for on your thank you page. There’s no guarantee it will improve your position in the SERPs, but it might influence it.&nbsp;</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Upsell a Product or Service&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Paid traffic is fast becoming an integral part of many online marketing campaigns.&nbsp;</p>



<p>And for good reason:&nbsp;</p>



<p>It’s highly effective.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Facebook Advertising, for instance, has been known to deliver a 5, 10—even <a href="https://www.facebook.com/business/success/aurum-brothers" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">13x return on investment</a> for e-commerce stores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But let’s be honest, paid traffic is expensive.&nbsp;</p>



<p>And if you’re not recouping your costs when acquiring a new lead, you’re losing money.</p>



<p>So, how do you ensure you don’t break the bank?</p>



<p><em>Offer a self-liquidating offer.</em></p>



<p>Simply put, <strong>a self-liquidating offer is a low-ticket item that covers your ad spends.&nbsp;</strong></p>



<p><a href="http://www.digitalmarketer.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Digital Marketer</a> offers self-liquidating offers on many of their thank you pages to not only recoup their ad costs but also to convert new subscribers into customers:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="530" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-1024x530.png" alt="Market Research Blueprint" class="wp-image-91220" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-1024x530.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-300x155.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-768x397.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-380x197.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-600x310.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-760x393.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-740x383.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23-385x199.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image15-23.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Granted, you won’t convert everyone (not yet, anyway), but you will break-even on some of your new acquisitions.&nbsp;</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway.</strong> Offer a self-liquidating thank you offer on your confirmation page if you’re paying for traffic.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Encourage Engagement&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>We all have a need to connect.&nbsp;</p>



<p>We want to meet with like-minded people and most importantly, feel like we belong&#8230;</p>



<p>And there’s no better way to feel like we belong than joining an online community.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The problem, though, is rarely, if ever, do you get a chance to interact with the tens of or hundreds of thousands of other readers a blog prides itself on.</p>



<p>That is unless you get an immediate introduction when you sign up.</p>



<p>When you join Derek Halpern’s community at <a href="http://socialtriggers.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Social Triggers</a>, you’re asked to “Like” his Facebook page and introduce yourself (notice the <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">social proof</a> to coax you further):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-1024x575.png" alt="Facebook Community" class="wp-image-91160" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image1-26.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>From there, Derek asks his readers questions on his Facebook page, further nurturing his relationship with his community:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="507" height="452" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24.png" alt="Facebook Post" class="wp-image-91200" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24.png 507w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-300x267.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-380x339.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-56x50.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-220x196.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image10-24-385x343.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px" /></figure></div>



<p>Do this consistently, and you build a thriving community of loyal readers and customers.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Include a Facebook or <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://disqus.com/" target="_blank">Disqus</a> comment box on your thank you page and ask a question to encourage engagement.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Conduct a Survey</strong></h2>



<p>Surveying your audience gives you great insight into what makes your audience tick. You learn about their goals, desires, and pain points which, in turn, helps you craft highly-targeted marketing messages.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>The problem, though. is many businesses get it <em>wrong</em>.</p>



<p>At best, they ask the wrong questions and at worse, they ask on an overpopulated platform (like Facebook).</p>



<p>What savvy business owners do, instead, is ask readers <em>immediately</em> after they’ve expressed an interest in their business.</p>



<p>After all, if you join a company’s newsletter, you probably have a problem top of mind.</p>



<p><a href="http://neilpatel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Neil Patel</a> knows this better than anyone.</p>



<p>When you enroll in Neil’s webinar (his lead magnet), he redirects you to a thank you page where he invites you to complete a short survey:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="656" height="650" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14.png" alt="Complete A Short Survey" class="wp-image-91240" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14.png 656w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-300x297.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-150x150.png 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-380x377.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-600x595.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-35x35.png 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-50x50.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-495x490.png 495w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-220x218.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-385x381.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/image20-14-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 656px) 100vw, 656px" /></figure></div>



<p>While Neil is mostly qualifying prospects for a strategy call, he’s still getting valuable feedback from his readers on what they’re struggling with and how he can help.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Takeaway</strong>. Ask your readers what their goals and struggles are and build your content marketing strategy around what they’re looking to learn more about.&nbsp;</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>






