										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>7 Nonprofit Email Examples That’ll Help You Drive More Donations</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Nonprofit Email Examples [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-97963" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Nonprofit-Email-Examples-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ed8e2e99a8a5" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Email open rates are on the decline. According to one report, the average open rate dropped to </span><a href="https://www.superoffice.com/blog/email-open-rates" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">22.1 percent</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> in 2019 (a decrease of 8% compared to 2018).</span></p>
</div>






<p>That’s the bad news.</p>



<p>The good news is, for nonprofits, open rates are the highest they’ve ever been at <a href="https://mailchimp.com/resources/email-marketing-benchmarks/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">25.18 percent</a>.</p>



<p>If, then, you’re an employee for a nonprofit organization, there are ample opportunities to drive more donations with email.</p>



<p>In this post, I’ll share seven nonprofits email examples you can use to ask for donations, directly or otherwise.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f3eb323036" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
