<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Ask Subscribers to Give Thanks</strong></h2>



<p><a href="https://www.rescue.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The International Rescue Committee</a> (IRC) is a nonprofit that helps people whose lives and livelihoods are shattered by conflict and disaster to survive, recover, and regain control of their future.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="522" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-1024x522.png" alt="Rescue.org Page" class="wp-image-97935" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-1024x522.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-300x153.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-768x391.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-1536x783.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-380x194.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-600x306.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-760x387.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-1440x734.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-740x377.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-220x112.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4-385x196.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image20-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In one recent email, the IRC invited me to thank health workers in Syria by sending a card.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="689" height="723" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4.png" alt="You Can Send A Thank You" class="wp-image-97899" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4.png 689w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-286x300.png 286w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-380x399.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-600x630.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-33x35.png 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-467x490.png 467w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-220x231.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image11-4-385x404.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px" /></figure></div>



<p>In that email was a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">call-to-action</a> (CTA) framed in several different ways, such as “Thank health workers in Syria,” to “Send a card.”&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="268" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-1024x268.png" alt="Send A Card" class="wp-image-97947" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-1024x268.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-300x79.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-768x201.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-380x99.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-600x157.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-760x199.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-134x35.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-191x50.png 191w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-740x194.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-220x58.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4-385x101.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image23-4.png 1070w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked “Send a card,” the IRC took me to a page on their website where I could add my note of thanks and support.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-1024x510.png" alt="Send Thanks To Health Workers" class="wp-image-97951" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image24-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But here’s where it gets interesting. After entering my name, email, and note, the nonprofit took me to a second page, where I could give a tax-deductible “gift.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-1024x510.png" alt="Thank You For Your Message" class="wp-image-97895" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image10-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Note the progress bar. This wasn’t on the previous page.&nbsp;</em></p>





<p>While a percentage of visitors are likely to leave at this stage, a decent percentage will still donate. Why? Because the IRC is using the <em>foot-in-the-door technique</em>.</p>



<p>In short, <strong>the foot-in-the-door technique is when you get someone to comply with a large request by first asking them to comply with a smaller request.</strong></p>



<p>The IRC first asks you to click through in an email. Then, they invite you to add a note of thanks and support. After, they ask for a donation. There&#8217;s sunk cost at this stage. You&#8217;re more likely to give than if the IRC asked outright from the start.</p>



<p>Our research of 10+ billion popup sessions found similar results. When looking at <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/multistep">multistep popups</a>, we saw <strong>popups with a second step, see a staggering </strong><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/popup-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>76 percent</strong></a><strong> of its subscribers input more information.</strong></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="960" height="791" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4.png" alt="One Step Versus Multistep Campaigns" class="wp-image-97907" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-300x247.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-768x633.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-380x313.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-600x494.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-760x626.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-61x50.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-595x490.png 595w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-220x181.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image13-4-385x317.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></figure></div>



<p>Bottom line? Ask subscribers to give thanks to a cause related to your organization. Then, invite them to give. A decent percentage will follow through.</p>





<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Offer Gift Matching</strong></h2>



<p>If you&#8217;ve read my post on <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/nonprofit-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">nonprofit popup examples</a>, you&#8217;ll know that a great way to drive more donations is by offering gift matching. This is when a nonprofit leverages corporate sponsors or philanthropists to “match” a donor&#8217;s contribution.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.alz.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Alzheimer&#8217;s Association</a> exemplifies gift matching nicely. In one recent email, the nonprofit offered to match donations up to $450,000, but only for a <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/limited-time-offers" target="_blank">limited time</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="893" height="770" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4.png" alt="Limited Time Match Donation Email" class="wp-image-97887" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4.png 893w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-300x259.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-768x662.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-380x328.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-600x517.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-760x655.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-568x490.png 568w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-220x190.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image8-4-385x332.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 893px) 100vw, 893px" /></figure></div>



<p>Here, the nonprofit expertly:</p>



<ol><li><strong>Frames the donation as a gift.</strong> A donation is about you. A gift, by contrast, is about someone else. The lesson is clear: avoid appealing to the reader’s wallet; instead, appeal to their emotions.</li><li><strong>Uses bullets to convey where the donation will go.</strong> Rather than asking for a donation outright, the Alzheimer’s Association prefaces its request by overcoming a common objection: Where does my donation go?</li><li><strong>Anchors a suggested donation.</strong> This not only nudges potential donors to give more, but it also removes the number of choices they have to make.</li></ol>



<p>If you wanted to build an email like this further, you could make a popup that targeted visitors coming from that specific campaign.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Let’s use the Alzheimer’s Association email as an example. If a reader clicked through in the email, the nonprofit took them to a donation page.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="522" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-1024x522.png" alt="Gift Amount Donation Page" class="wp-image-97931" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-1024x522.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-300x153.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-768x391.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-1536x783.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-380x194.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-600x306.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-760x387.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-1440x734.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-740x377.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-220x112.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4-385x196.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image19-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>However, there was nothing to prompt them further if they bounced. What the nonprofit could have done was make an <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/exit-intent-popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">exit-intent popup</a>, reiterating the email’s message.</p>



<p>Here’s an example, courtesy of Seray:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="682" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-1024x682.png" alt="Exit-Intent Popup Example" class="wp-image-97883" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-1024x682.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-300x200.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-768x511.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-380x253.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-600x400.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-760x506.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-53x35.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-75x50.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-736x490.png 736w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-220x146.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4-385x256.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image7-4.png 1224w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>You can’t always offer gift matching; that’s part of the appeal, of course. But when you can, make sure to go all out and use every tool at your disposal, popup included.</p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Incentivize Donations</strong></h2>



<p>Whether it’s a free product or even a discount, people love freebies. It makes perfect sense, then, that nonprofits sometimes activate potential donors with gifts.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The <a href="https://www.hrc.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Human Rights Campaign</a> (HRC) is one such example.&nbsp;</p>



<p>After signing up for its emails, the nonprofit offered me a free tee-shirt if I donated. The kicker, of course, was that the freebie was available for one day only.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="885" height="650" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4.png" alt="Send Me A Shirt CTA" class="wp-image-97875" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4.png 885w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-768x564.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-380x279.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-600x441.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-760x558.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-667x490.png 667w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-220x162.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image5-4-385x283.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 885px) 100vw, 885px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked the image, I landed on a donations page with a headline that read, “Join by MIDNIGHT,” reiterating to the urgency outlined in the email.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-1024x510.png" alt="Join By Midnight Gift" class="wp-image-97927" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image18-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The pièce de résistance, though, was the checkbox at the bottom of the order form, offering to automatically renew my subscription annually at the time of donation.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-1024x510.png" alt="Annual Membership" class="wp-image-97871" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image4-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Like the IRC asking subscribers to give thanks and then asking for a donation, incentivizing donations can feel like bait-and-switch if misused.&nbsp;</p>



<p>It’s important, then, that, when offering freebies, be sure to mention that the freebie comes with donations above a certain amount. Failing to do so will risk leaving a bad taste in your subscribers&#8217; mouth, and even hurt your nonprofit&#8217;s reputation.&nbsp;</p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Gift on Someone’s Behalf</strong></h2>



<p>One challenge that befalls many shoppers come <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/seasonal-marketing-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">holiday season</a> is not knowing what to buy loved ones. But for charities looking to boost seasonal donations, it might be the perfect solution.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.stbaldricks.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The St Baldricks Foundation</a> describes itself as “a charity committed to supporting the most promising research to find cures for childhood cancers and give survivors long and healthy lives.”</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-1024x510.png" alt="DFY" class="wp-image-97939" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image21-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In one recent email, the nonprofit offered subscribers a chance to send a mother’s day card hand-drawn by one of the charity’s ambassadors, Avery, a cancer survivor.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="565" height="745" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4.png" alt="Mother Day Campaign" class="wp-image-97903" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4.png 565w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-228x300.png 228w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-380x501.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-372x490.png 372w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-220x290.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image12-4-385x508.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 565px) 100vw, 565px" /></figure></div>



<p>After choosing to “send an ecard,” subscribers were taken to a page inviting them to “give the gift of childhood cancer research” by sending an ecard that let their mother know how much they meant to them.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-1024x510.png" alt="Mothers Day Gift That Gives Back" class="wp-image-97879" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image6-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When subscribers clicked the CTA, “Make a donation &amp; send ecard,” they were taken to a donation page where they could make a one time or monthly contribution.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-1024x510.png" alt="Donation Page" class="wp-image-97867" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image3-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As with giving thanks or gift matching, inviting subscribers to donate on someone’s behalf shifts the onus from the subscriber to someone else, and in doing so, makes it easier for the subscriber to donate.</p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Tell a Story</strong></h2>



<p>Who are you more likely to give money to? Abdi, a three-year-old starving orphan living, in war-torn Yemen, or a malnourished family living in identical conditions?</p>



<p>If you answered the former, you’re not alone. Due to what’s known as the <a href="https://www.classy.org/blog/6-fundraising-psychology-hacks/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">identifiable victim effect</a>, we’re more likely to donate to a cause with a single, identifiable victim than we are a large group of the same need.&nbsp;</p>



<p>One nonprofit that leverages the identifiable victim effect through expertly told stories is <a href="https://www.savethechildren.net/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Save the Children</a>, an organization that saves and improves children&#8217;s lives around the world.</p>



<p>In one recent email, the nonprofit told a story about Waleed, an eight-year-old who suffered partial blindness due to an airstrike. (Note the specificity.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="870" height="300" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4.png" alt="Save The Children Story" class="wp-image-97891" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4.png 870w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-300x103.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-768x265.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-380x131.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-600x207.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-760x262.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-102x35.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-145x50.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-740x255.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image9-4-385x133.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px" /></figure></div>



<p>The email weaves masterful storytelling with hard-hitting realism before inviting the reader to donate to ensure the nonprofit is able to help children like Waleed moving forward.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="900" height="190" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4.png" alt="Story Ending" class="wp-image-97919" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4.png 900w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-300x63.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-768x162.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-380x80.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-600x127.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-760x160.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-166x35.png 166w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-237x50.png 237w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-740x156.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image16-4-385x81.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></figure></div>



<p>When I clicked the CTA, the nonprofit took me to, you guessed it, a donations page, where I could make a one time or monthly contribution.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-1024x510.png" alt="Save The Children Donation Page" class="wp-image-97859" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image1-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you wanted to build on this email further, you could create a dedicated landing page and popup (similar to the above example), reiterating the email’s message.</p>



<p>I don’t think I’m alone when I say it would have been nice to see Waleed, the boy mentioned in the email, on the landing page as a reminder of why I chose to donate, to begin with.</p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Give Donations Context</strong></h2>



<p>Unlike other industries, nonprofits have fewer objections they need to overcome or raise to begin with. There is one objection, however, that comes up regardless of size, reputation, or importance:</p>



<p><em>Where does my donation go?</em></p>



<p>Donors want to know what percentage of their giving will go to support the mission of the nonprofit, as opposed to administrative expenses. And rightfully so.</p>



<p>To overcome that objection, some nonprofits, such as <a href="https://www.helpforheroes.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Help for Heroes</a>, not only mention where a donor&#8217;s gift will go but also how much is needed.</p>



<p>In this email example, the nonprofit suggests three possible donations, based on how much the donor can afford to give and where they want it to go.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="875" height="530" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4.png" alt="Context For Donations" class="wp-image-97923" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4.png 875w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-300x182.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-768x465.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-380x230.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-600x363.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-760x460.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-740x448.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-220x133.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image17-4-385x233.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 875px) 100vw, 875px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a href="https://reallygoodemails.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">ReallyGoodEmails</a></em></p>





<p>Giving donations context is better suited for emails that ask for donations directly. However, it&#8217;s still worth experimenting with for other emails, especially if a donor&#8217;s gift can be used in a myriad of ways.</p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Recruit Volunteers</strong></h2>



<p>Most of the email examples we’ve covered so far deal with driving more donations. However, for some nonprofits, asking for volunteers is as important.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.patagonia.com/actionworks/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Patagonia Action Works</a> is one such example.</p>



<p>In one email I found, the nonprofit invited subscribers to put their skills to use and volunteer.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="654" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-1024x654.png" alt="Volunteer Your Skills For Our Planet" class="wp-image-97911" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-1024x654.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-300x191.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-768x490.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-380x243.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-600x383.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-760x485.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-78x50.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-740x472.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-220x140.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4-385x246.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image14-4.png 1175w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When subscribers chose to “get involved,” they were taken to a page where they could learn more about helping out.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-1024x510.png" alt="Problems That You Can Help To Solve" class="wp-image-97863" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image2-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>What I liked most, though, was the range of choice the nonprofit affords its readers. Rather than inviting the reader to submit a form, it allows them to filter their preferences by issue and then learn more.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="510" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-1024x510.png" alt="The Issue Description" class="wp-image-97915" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-1024x510.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-600x299.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-1440x717.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-100x50.png 100w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4-385x192.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image15-4.png 1901w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Granted, the range of choice varies from one organization to another, but it’s still a nice afterthought.</em></p>





<p>If you wanted to build on this email further, you could make a popup inviting returning visitors to get involved, as <a href="https://www.mencap.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Mencap</a> does on its homepage.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="509" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-1024x509.png" alt="Mencap Teaser Inviting Volunteers" class="wp-image-97943" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-1024x509.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-768x381.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-1536x763.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-600x298.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-760x377.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-1440x715.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-740x367.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/image22-4.png 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


