<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Apparel Email Marketing 101: 11 Must-Have Emails (2021)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="438" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-1024x438.jpg" alt="Apparel Email Marketing Examples [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-82714" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-1024x438.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-1536x657.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-2048x876.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-600x257.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-1440x616.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Apparel-Email-Marketing-Examples-Wordpress-385x165.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e830b00817c7" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The fashion and apparel industry is exploding right now. According to <a href="https://www.shopify.com/plus/industry-reports/fashion-and-apparel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">a new report by Shopify</a>, “Experts predict that the e-commerce segment of fashion and apparel will increase at a compound annual rate of 10.6 percent from $408 billion in 2017 to <em>more than $706 billion</em> by 2022” (emphasis mine).<br data-rich-text-line-break="true" /></span></p>
</div>






<p>With the decline of ad revenue and the rise of third-party-cookie restrictions, email, as a marketing channel, continues to be more important than ever for online retailers.<br></p>



<p>So, with that in mind, I want to share 9 <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/apparel-subject-lines" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">apparel email</a> marketing examples you can model for your business. These emails will help turn readers into subscribers into buyers and with a little luck, return customers into brand loyalists.<br></p>


