<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Communicate Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR)</strong></h2>



<p>More companies than ever before are engaging in socially responsible activities.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And for good reason.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Corporate social responsibility, or CSR, not only increases employee engagement, but it also increases how customers rate a company’s products.<br></p>



<p>When subjects <a href="https://academic.oup.com/jcr/article/41/6/1412/2379575" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">in one study</a> were told that the wine they sampled supported a charity, they rated the wine as tasting much better than those who had not been given the additional information.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>According to Robert Cialdini, who shares the study in the book, <em>Yes! 60 Secrets from The Science of Persuasion</em>, there are two keys to making a CSR program work.<br></p>



<p>The first is to persuade prospects and buyers that a CSR program is worthwhile. The second challenge is to find ways to publicize the charitable deeds and socially responsible activities that you practice without bragging or appearing self-righteous.<br></p>



<p>One of my favorite CSR examples that illustrates both keys comes from a recent email from <a href="https://bombas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Bombas</a>.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="771" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-1024x771.png" alt="Bombas CRS Email" class="wp-image-82746" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-1024x771.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-300x226.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-768x578.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-1536x1157.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-380x286.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-600x452.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-760x572.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-1440x1084.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-66x50.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-651x490.png 651w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-220x166.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email-385x290.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-CRS-Email.png 1781w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Not only are <a href="https://goodplusfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">GOOD+</a> and <a href="https://careergear.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Career Geara</a> worthwhile causes (both aim to combat multi-generational poverty), but Bombas makes the good deed <em>reciprocal</em>. Bombas donates $25,000 to each organization with each purchase and the customer contributes to not one, but <em>two </em>worth causes. What’s not to like?<br></p>



<p>While CSR activities have been found to increase customer loyalty and enhance employee engagement, it’s important to mention that abusing it for financial gain is not recommended. Anything otherwise is guaranteed to leave a bitter taste in your customers’ mouth.&nbsp;<br></p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Run a Giveaway</strong></h2>



<p>Let’s face it:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>People love freebies.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>It doesn’t matter whether it’s a $100 gift card, or fully-stacked skincare fridge, as <a href="https://freemanbeauty.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Freeman Beauty</a> recently offered, we love getting something for nothing.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="931" height="595" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway.png" alt="Freeman Beauty Giveaway" class="wp-image-82766" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway.png 931w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-300x192.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-768x491.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-380x243.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-600x383.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-760x486.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-78x50.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-740x473.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-220x141.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Freeman-Beauty-Giveaway-385x246.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 931px) 100vw, 931px" /></figure></div>



<p>While many giveaways often take place on platforms like Instagram, that doesn’t mean you can’t drive traffic to a giveaway, off-site or otherwise, using email.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.bando.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ban.do</a> recently ran a giveaway on Instagram and invited their email subscribers to get involved by including the following in the email footer.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="423" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-1024x423.png" alt="Ban.Do Giveaway" class="wp-image-82734" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-1024x423.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-300x124.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-768x317.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-1536x635.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-380x157.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-600x248.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-760x314.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-1440x595.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-85x35.png 85w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-121x50.png 121w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-740x306.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-220x91.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway-385x159.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Ban.Do-Giveaway.png 1790w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The goal, as is with any giveaway, is to create <em>virality</em>. The more people share the giveaway with others, the greater its exposure. So, if you’re following best practice and telling subscribers to tag friends in the post, why not invite them to forward the email, too? It might not make a big difference, but it’s <em>a</em> difference nonetheless.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Instagram isn’t the only platform for running giveaways, of course. You can (and should) run them on your website, too—but not until you’ve read Seray’s guide: <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/giveaway-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">7 Creative (On-Site) Giveaway Ideas You Can Try Today</a>.<br></p>





<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Encourage Buyer Engagement</strong></h2>



<p>We all know the importance of <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email marketing</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>You’ve no doubt read the figures and agree that, for the time being, at least, it’s the best marketing channel when it comes to delivering a return on investment (ROI).<br></p>



<p>But that return is dependent, by and large, on the extent subscribers open and engage with your emails.<br></p>



<p>That might be replying to emails, redeeming coupons, clicking-through to learn more about promotions, and more.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Given its importance, then, not to mention the ubiquitous of inbox overcrowding, inviting readers to open, click through and engage with your emails is crucial for apparel marketers.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.charlottetilbury.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Charlotte Tilbury</a> know this better than any retailer.<br></p>



<p>They likely experience cart abandonment like many online retailers, so, to minimize it, they make a concentrated effort to reach out <em>before</em> you even get a chance to abandon your cart.<br></p>



<p>And it’s truly something to marvel at.<br></p>



<p>After browsing one of their <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">product pages</a> and exiting without buying anything, I got the following email in my inbox.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="815" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-1024x815.png" alt="Charlotte Tilbury Email Example" class="wp-image-82758" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-1024x815.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-300x239.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-768x611.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-380x302.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-600x477.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-760x605.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-63x50.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-616x490.png 616w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-220x175.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example-385x306.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Charlotte-Tilbury-Email-Example.png 1320w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Personalized. Timely. Impressive, even. It’s a breath of fresh air in my otherwise over-crowded inbox. After all, they’re right—I <em>was</em> looking (for a friend, I swear).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And given its relevant copy and clear <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">call-to-action</a>, it’s tough not to engage with.<br></p>



<p>Bottom line?<br></p>



<p>Invite subscribers to interact with your emails, early and often. Not only will it increase your <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/email-deliverability" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">email deliverability</a>, but it will invite subscribers to keep you top of mind, longer. And that’s only a good thing.&nbsp;<br></p>





<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Promote Popular Products</strong></h2>



<p>“People love to buy but hate to be sold to,” at least, that’s what conventional sales training suggests.<br></p>



<p>But research from a report by <a href="https://marketingsherpa.com/article/chart/how-customers-want-promo-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Marketing Sherpa</a> suggests otherwise. In their findings, a staggering 93 percent of people said they would like to receive promotional emails from companies they do business with.<br></p>



<p>While numbers like the above vary from one industry to another, it does iterate the importance of giving buyers what they want when they want it.<br></p>



<p>However, as I’ll discuss in a moment, there’s more to product promotion than blasting out an email to all subscribers.<br></p>





<h3><strong>i. Product Launch</strong></h3>



<p>With countless product launches bombarding buyers on what feels like a weekly, if not daily basis, one would imagine that those brands are doing their best to differentiate themselves from their competitors.<br></p>



<p>But opening any recent product launch email suggests otherwise.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Generic, unimaginative and rarely enticing, many emails leave little to the imagination. And those that do, fail to get the buyer to take any action.<br></p>



<p>One online retailer that does distinguish itself, fortunately, is <a href="https://huckberry.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Huckberry</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="573" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-1024x573.png" alt="Huckberry Product Promotion" class="wp-image-82770" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-1024x573.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-300x168.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-768x430.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-1536x860.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-380x213.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-600x336.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-760x425.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-1440x806.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-740x414.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-220x123.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Huckberry-Product-Promotion.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Going beyond general announcement and uninspired imagery, Huckberry leverages <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/persuasive-copywriting-techniques" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">benefit-driven copy</a> to invite readers to click through and learn more.<br></p>



<p>Adding a backstory to a product launch—why you’re launching it, who it’s for, the benefits it offers—calls for greater effort, of course. But given <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/story-based-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">our experience writing story-based emails</a>, it’s an effort worth prioritizing.<br></p>





<h3><strong>ii. Seasonal Sale</strong></h3>



<p>Countless factors go into influencing a product’s revenue performance—target buyer, price elasticity, market competition, to name a few.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But one that’s often overlooked, is <em>seasonality</em>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Take a recent email I got from luggage retailer, <a href="https://www.awaytravel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Away</a>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-1024x646.png" alt="Away Product Promotion" class="wp-image-82722" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-1024x646.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-300x189.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-768x485.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-1536x970.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-600x379.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-760x480.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-1440x909.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-740x467.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion-385x243.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Product-Promotion.png 1790w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Knowing the demand for their products is likely to spike before prospects go away on their summer vacation, Away invite readers to “seize the season,” and “explore the collection” before vacating.<br></p>



<p>Of course, that’s not to say Away, nor you, for that matter, can’t market your products off-season. But it is something to keep in mind when scheduling promotional emails.<br></p>





<h3><strong>iii. Just Because</strong></h3>



<p>Buyers are dubious enough when it comes to buying discounted offers. But they’re <em>especially</em> cautious when a reason isn’t given.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Failing to justify a promotion, then, be it due to launching a new product launch or clearing out last season’s bestsellers, leaves prospects to jump to their own conclusions. And that’s rarely a good thing.<br></p>



<p>So, if you don’t have a reason for running a promotion, do you need to forgo it completely?<br></p>



<p>Not necessarily.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In the now-famous <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/232505985_The_mindlessness_of_ostensibly_thoughtful_action_The_role_of_placebic_information_in_interpersonal_interaction" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">copy machine study</a>, Ellen Langer and her colleagues found that people waiting to use a copy machine were more likely to let a stranger cut in line if they give a reason—regardless of its legitimacy.<br></p>



<p>When the stranger asked to cut in front due to being in a rush, 94 percent of people complied. But when the reason, <em>“because I need to make some copies,”</em> was given, <strong>93 percent of people obliged.</strong><br></p>



<p>To bypass people’s skepticism to promotions, then, give a reason—any reason—when running a promotion. I call this the “just because” strategy: you’re running a product or offering a discount “just because.”<br></p>



<p>Take <a href="https://www.ayr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">AYR</a>, for instance.<br></p>



<p>They recently offered their subscribers $40 off dresses. The reason they gave? Because <em>“it’s too damn hot out”</em>:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="527" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-1024x527.png" alt="AYR Product Promotion" class="wp-image-82730" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-1024x527.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-300x154.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-768x395.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-380x196.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-600x309.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-760x391.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-1440x741.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-97x50.png 97w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-740x381.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion-385x198.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/AYR-Product-Promotion.png 1515w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>You don’t always need a meaningful reason to run a promotion. “Just because” is often more than enough.<br></p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Drive Last-Minute Purchases</strong></h2>



<p>Decades ago, selling through direct mail was a gargantuan feat.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Not only did you have to convince prospects to buy your product, but you also had to get them to complete a form and mail it off.<br></p>



<p>(Assuming, of course, they were still interested by the time they got to the post office.)<br></p>



<p>Today, thankfully, making a purchase is as easy as the click of a button. But with greater ease, has come an unintended consequence to put off buying until the last possible moment.<br></p>



<p>Following on from the earlier section, if you’re running a new promotion, sending a final, last chance email is a no brainer if you want to convert more buyers.<br></p>



<p>We’ve written about <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/scarcity-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">scarcity</a> and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/fomo-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">FOMO</a> before, so I won’t repeat myself here. What I will say, though, is as always, honesty is key. If “Time’s almost up!” as it was for a recent <a href="https://www.asicstiger.com/us/en-us/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">ASICS Tiger</a> promotion, so be it.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="582" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-1024x582.png" alt="ASICS Tiger Last Chance Email" class="wp-image-82718" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-1024x582.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-300x171.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-768x437.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-1536x874.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-380x216.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-600x341.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-760x432.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-1440x819.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-740x421.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-220x125.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email-385x219.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ASICS-Tiger-Last-Chance-Email.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And if it’s not?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Avoid lying at all costs.<br></p>





<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Survey Your Subscribers</strong></h2>



<p>If you’re in the habit of surveying new customers, you already know their inputs are worth more than their weight in gold.<br></p>



<p>But what about non-buyers? Can you mine value out of their insights, too?<br></p>



<p>Aside from more common inquiries like email preferences, surveying prospects gives you feedback on customer service improvements, reason(s) for purchase, and even online course creation.<br></p>



<p>Yes, you read correctly: more e-commerce brands are now expanding into online courses and using their audience’s insight to help build them.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>To offer an example, <a href="https://fab.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Fab</a> recently asked for my inputs for a yoga-based online course they’re creating.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="542" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-1024x542.png" alt="Fab Survey Email" class="wp-image-82762" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-1024x542.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-300x159.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-768x407.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-380x201.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-600x318.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-760x403.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-1440x763.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-66x35.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-94x50.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-740x392.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-220x117.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email-385x204.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Fab-Survey-Email.png 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>You might not have intentions to create an online course, but take note: asking subscribers what they want—and repeating back to them what they want in your copy—goes a long way.<br></p>





<h2 id="8"><strong>8. Show Your Appreciation</strong></h2>



<p>There’s an old joke that the comedian Rodney Dangerfield would tell about his wife: <em>“With my wife, I don&#8217;t get no respect. I made a toast on her birthday to ‘the best woman a man ever had.’ The waiter joined me.”</em><br></p>



<p>Humor aside, no one, buyers, prospects, or otherwise, want to feel disrespected or underappreciated. When it comes to considering a purchase, we want to feel like the brand we’re thinking about buying from has our best interests at heart.<br></p>



<p>What better way to show you care, then, than with an email offering subscribers a discount on their birthday?<br></p>



<p><a href="https://www.topshop.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Topshop</a> is known for their rapid growth in recent years, but what they might not be known for is their effort to make their audience feel special. Take a look at how they welcome and wow new subscribers. First, they tease a “special treat” in their email popup copy.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="490" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-1024x490.png" alt="Topshop Popup Example" class="wp-image-82782" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-1024x490.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-1536x735.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-600x287.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-1440x689.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-740x354.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Popup-Example.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Then, on your birthday, they email you to wish you many happy returns&#8230;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="620" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-1024x620.png" alt="Topshop Birthday Email 2" class="wp-image-82774" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-1024x620.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-300x182.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-768x465.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-1536x930.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-380x230.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-600x363.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-760x460.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-1440x872.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-740x448.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-220x133.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2-385x233.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-2.png 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;before offering a 20% discount.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="629" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-1024x629.png" alt="Topshop Birthday Email" class="wp-image-82778" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-1024x629.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-300x184.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-768x472.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-1536x943.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-380x233.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-600x368.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-760x467.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-1440x884.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-740x454.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-220x135.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email-385x236.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Topshop-Birthday-Email.png 1915w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s nice for subscribers, it’s also clever on Topshop’s part. They know many people are gifted money on their birthday … and are likely to splurge it on a brand that acknowledges it (if, that is, they’re given a little incentive).<br></p>





<h2 id="9"><strong>9. Ask for Referrals</strong></h2>



<p>With as much as 74 percent of consumers identifying word-of-mouth as a key influencer in their purchasing decision, as reported by <a href="http://www.ogilvy.com/News/Press-Releases/June-2014-Consumer-behavior-comes-under-the-spotlight-in-new-study.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Ogilvy</a>, it’s no surprise that many brands invest in referral programs.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But it’s important to understand that there’s more to referral marketing than asking for a recommendation—timing, as well as incentivizing the request, is as important.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The latter, for the most part, is obvious when you think about it. After having tried on, worn and justified their purchases, buyers are more likely to refer a friend (especially with a little prodding).&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what about incentives? Well, there are a few approaches to consider.<br></p>



<p>One common approach is to offer a percentage discount as <a href="https://bonobos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Bonobos</a> do:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="439" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-1024x439.png" alt="Bonobos Referral Email" class="wp-image-82754" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-1024x439.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-300x129.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-768x329.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-1536x659.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-380x163.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-600x257.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-760x326.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-1440x617.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-740x317.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email-385x165.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bonobos-Referral-Email.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Another, more creative approach, is to follow Away’s example and offer a dollar amount discount:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="781" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-781x1024.png" alt="Away Referral Email" class="wp-image-82726" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-781x1024.png 781w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-229x300.png 229w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-768x1007.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-1171x1536.png 1171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-380x498.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-600x787.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-760x997.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-374x490.png 374w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-220x289.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai-385x505.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Away-Referral-Emai.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 781px) 100vw, 781px" /></figure></div>



<p>My favorite approach, though, and one I’ve written about before, is offering a <em>physical</em> incentive as <a href="https://bombas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Bombas</a> does:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="555" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2.png" alt="Bombas Referral Email" class="wp-image-82750" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2.png 555w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-290x300.png 290w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-380x394.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-34x35.png 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-48x50.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-473x490.png 473w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-220x228.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Bombas-Referral-Email-2-385x399.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 555px) 100vw, 555px" /></figure></div>



<p>There’s no right or wrong way to incentivize referrals and you will need to experiment what resonates with your buyers. But given the effectiveness of referral marketing, it’s something you need to consider if you haven’t already.&nbsp;<br></p>


