<h1 class="has-text-align-center">Popups Are Dead. Wrong. Here’s What We Found from Analyzing 1+ Billion Popups (Original Research)</h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/list-building" rel="category tag">List Building</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Popup Statistics [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-94307" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Popup-Statistics-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5eb117c70e151" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re an online retailer, you’re likely using <a href="https://sleeknote.com/email-popup">email popups</a> to </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies"><span style="font-weight: 400;">grow your email list</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and </span><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-recommendation-popups"><span style="font-weight: 400;">recommend popular products</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
</div>






<p>But what you might not know is how to optimize those popups for maximum conversions&#8230;</p>



<p>That changes now.</p>



<p>In this article, I’ll share how to create a high-converting popup, element by element.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The best part? We based our findings on real numbers we pulled from our top-performing customers, which, all in all, accounted for 1+ billion popup views. (That’s not a typo.)</p>



<p>Let’s get started.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e8b30df2996f" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle"></p>
