<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>



<p>Popups are ugly, intrusive, and above all, hurt the user experience…</p>



<p>But only if you ignore the best practices I’ve outlined above.</p>



<p>The popup statistics in this post have shown you how to optimize your popups for maximum conversion.</p>



<p>Now it’s time for you to make the changes, or <a href="https://sleeknote.com/popup-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">get started with your first popup</a>.</p>



