										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>E-Commerce Email Marketing 101: 11 Must-Have Emails (2021)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/email-marketing" rel="category tag">Email Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Email Marketing [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-91952" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Email-Marketing-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e9db55035c46" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re like most e-commerce marketers, you’re investing in email marketing.</span></p>
</div>






<p>You’re <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">growing your email list</a>, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">sending well-written email campaigns</a> and <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-personalization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">engaging return visitors</a> with personalized on-site messages.</p>



<p>But as effective as email marketing is, it’s not enough on its own.</p>



<p>Why? Because <strong>e-commerce email marketing isn’t about the right strategy; it’s about the right </strong><strong><em>sequencing</em></strong><strong>.</strong></p>



<p>Mail the right emails at the wrong time to the wrong prospect, and people will opt out of your emails (or worse, move to a competitor).</p>



<p>But mail the right emails at the right time to the right prospects, and you won’t just have lifelong customers, you’ll have brand evangelists.</p>



<p>Today, I want to share 11 e-commerce marketing campaigns that will help you build a following of raving fans. Whether you’re looking to increase engagement, boost revenue, or reduce unsubscribes, there’s something for you in the post.</p>



<p>Let’s get started.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e6f3eb323036" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">FREE DOWNLOADABLE BONUS</p>
