										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>E-Commerce Copywriting 101: How to Write Killer Product Descriptions</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="240" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-1024x240.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Copywriting" class="wp-image-92711" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-1024x240.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-300x70.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-768x180.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-1536x360.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-2048x480.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-380x89.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-600x141.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-760x178.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-1440x338.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-149x35.jpg 149w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-213x50.jpg 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-740x173.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/E-Commerce-Copywriting-385x90.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5ea19a8f00b27" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There’s a game being played online every day… Only you might not realize it.</span></p>
</div>






<p>If you are, chances are you’re enjoying greater profits while working fewer hours than your competitors.&nbsp;</p>



<p>And if you’re not?</p>



<p>You’re wondering why your products aren’t flying off their digital shelves.</p>



<p>The game is simple:</p>



<p><em>How long can you keep visitors engaged on your site?&nbsp;</em></p>



<p>There are, of course, many ways to do that, but there’s one that’s more effective than any other:</p>



<p><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/persuasive-copywriting-techniques" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><em>Writing persuasive copy.</em></a></p>



<p>The truth is, you can have the best site design in the world, the best products, the best <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">value proposition</a> … but if you don’t have persuasive product copy, none of the above matters.&nbsp;</p>



<p>In this article, I’ll show you how many of the best e-commerce brands online engage and entice readers to make a purchase using proven <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/copywriting-examples" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">copywriting</a> principles. And most importantly, how you can, too.</p>



<p>Shall we?&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>


