<h2><strong>Casper Marketing: 14 Proven Growth Strategies You Need to Steal</strong></h2>



<p>Below are 14 strategies Casper used to grow their company. Not all of them will be relevant to you. That’s a given. So, to save time, I’ve added a table of contents so you can jump to the strategies that interest you most.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><a href="#1">1. Reinvent The Buying Experience</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Create an Unbeatable Guarantee</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Answer Your Target Market’s Questions (ToFu)</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. Create a Go-To Comparison Resource (MoFu)</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. Showcase All Reviews in One Place (BoFu)</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Build White-Hat Education Links with “The CSD Method”</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Publish Original Research (and Become a Go-To Authority in Your Marketplace)</a></p>



<p><a href="#8">8. Use “The Best-of Backlink Builder” (with a Twist)</a></p>



<p><a href="#9">9. Translate Your Ads to Capture New Markets</a></p>



<p><a href="#10">10. Try This Little-Known Trick to Monopolize Your Search Ads</a></p>



<p><a href="#11">11. Combine Advertising and Remarketing to Get More Leads for Your Online Store</a></p>



<p><a href="#12">12. Use This 3-Step Cart Abandonment Process to Recover Lost Sales</a></p>



<p><a href="#13">13. Turn Customers into Salespeople with This Replicable Referral Engine</a></p>



<p><a href="#14">14. Get Better Customer Reviews with This Simple, Yet Powerful Copy Hack</a></p>



<p>Ready? Let’s dive in.<br></p>





<h2><strong>Part 1: Positioning</strong></h2>



<p>Positioning is everything.<br></p>



<p>It’s how you capture the biggest market share and become a household name. And, how you build your strategy around your competition’s weaknesses.<br></p>



<p>Here’s how Casper is winning the battle for their buyers’ minds&#8230;<br></p>





<h2 id="1"><strong>Strategy #1: Reinvent The Buying Experience</strong></h2>



<p>Buying a mattress was once a complicated affair.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>First, you had to browse several furniture stores to compare prices. Then, you had to choose a type of mattress (open spring, pocket spring, etc.). More, you had to test its firmness depending on your preferred sleeping position, height, and weight. Next, you had to choose an appropriate size (single, double, king size, etc.). Finally, after making a decision, you had to negotiate with a pushy salesperson trying to upsell you.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>And that was just the beginning.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Once bought, you had to guide the delivery man through your home, praying he wouldn’t damage your new mattress before setting it down.<br></p>



<p>Today, it’s a VERY different experience.<br></p>



<p>While buying a mattress in-store is still common, Casper has reinvented what it means to buy a mattress.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Gone are the days of awkwardly lying on a mattress in front of a salesman and then waiting around all day for a delivery.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Today, with a few clicks of a mouse, you can order a mattress from the comfort of your home and have it delivered for free within a 60-minute window of your choice. (<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.cnbc.com/video/3000600328" target="_blank">Source</a>)</p>







<p>Casper’s reinvention of the buying experience runs throughout their marketing, beginning top-of-funnel with their Google search ads.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="247" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-1024x247.png" alt="Casper_s Google Search Ad" class="wp-image-86062" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-1024x247.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-300x73.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-768x186.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-380x92.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-600x145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-760x184.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-207x50.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-740x179.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Google-Search-Ad.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>As Lindsay Kaplan, Casper’s VP of communications and brand engagement said in one interview:<br></p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-style-large"><p><span class="has-inline-color has-plum-color">Our strategy from the start has been to change perceptions about mattress shopping and create a community around sleep in a playful and creative way, with a genuine voice. (<a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://nordic.businessinsider.com/how-the-200-million-startup-casper-is-looking-to-upend-advertising-2017-7/" target="_blank">Source</a>)</span></p></blockquote>



<p>Casper has reinvented the buying experience by capitalizing on the “mattress in a box” concept, a trend that’s seen a steady climb in recent years, particularly in the United States and Canada (more on that shortly).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-1024x491.png" alt="Mattress in a Box" class="wp-image-86162" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mattress-in-a-Box.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="346" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-1024x346.png" alt="Casper_s Interest by Region" class="wp-image-86074" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-1024x346.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-300x101.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-768x260.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-1536x519.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-380x129.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-600x203.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-760x257.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-1440x487.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-148x50.png 148w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-740x250.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-220x74.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region-385x130.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Interest-by-Region.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Buying a mattress in a box is exactly as it sounds. Once it arrives, you remove the mattress from the box and set it on your foundation while it’s still encased in plastic. Then, you remove the mattress from its plastic wrapping, give it 45 minutes to an hour to regain its shape, and you’re ready for a good night’s sleep.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Here it is in action:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe title="Unbox Better Sleep" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jhjW6JN6H00?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>Similar to companies like Apple, <strong>Casper has transformed something as mundane as unboxing their product into a memorable, share-worthy experience.</strong>&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>In fact, they even go as far as encouraging you to document your unboxing experience on their frequently asked questions (FAQ) page.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="462" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png" alt="Casper_s FAQ Page" class="wp-image-86046" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-768x347.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-600x271.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-760x343.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1440x650.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-740x334.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page-385x174.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-FAQ-Page.png 1485w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Unboxing, in and of itself, is another trend Casper has capitalized on, given its increased interest in recent years.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="442" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png" alt="Unboxing in Google Trends" class="wp-image-86190" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-300x129.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-768x331.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1536x662.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-380x164.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-600x259.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-760x328.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1440x621.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-740x319.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-385x166.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020