<p>Casper’s unboxing videos are so popular, they have millions of views on YouTube, alone, resulting in free publicity for the company.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png" alt="Casper Unboxing Video" class="wp-image-86026" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-2048x976.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-1440x686.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Unboxing-Video-385x183.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s no surprise then that 53.86% of Casper’s entire social traffic comes from YouTube (most of which comes from their <em>customer’s</em> videos rather than their own.)<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="259" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png" alt="Casper_s Social Traffic" class="wp-image-86122" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-300x76.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-768x194.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1536x388.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-380x96.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-600x152.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-760x192.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1440x364.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-139x35.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-198x50.png 198w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-740x187.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-220x56.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic-385x97.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Social-Traffic.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>When you reinvent the buying experience. People pay attention.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Ask yourself, “Can I reinvent the buying experience for my customers?” “Can I capitalize on a growing trend to help deliver that experience?” “Can I make every stage of the buying cycle memorable and share-worthy?”</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="2"><strong>Strategy #2: Create an Unbeatable Guarantee</strong></h2>



<p>Imagine, for a moment, you’re in a pet shop and your child is begging you for a puppy.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Unsure whether it’s a good idea, you say no.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>The salesperson, aware of this dynamic, proposes the following: “Take the puppy home over the weekend. If it’s too much responsibility, bring it back on Monday for a full refund, no questions asked.”<br></p>



<p>Secretly hoping that your child will lose interest by the end of the weekend, you agree to take the puppy home. Most of the time, you turn out to be right. The child <em>does</em> lose interest in the puppy—but you fall in love with it. By Sunday night, you want the puppy more than the child does. Ding. Ding.<br></p>



<p>The puppy-dog close, as it’s known, is one of the most effective closing techniques in the book. And, unsurprisingly, one Casper leverage throughout their marketing, notably with their unbeatable guarantee.<br></p>



<p>For each of their mattresses, Casper offers a risk-free 100-night free trial.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="448" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png" alt="Casper_s Guarantee" class="wp-image-86070" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-768x336.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-1536x672.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-600x263.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-760x333.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-1440x630.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-114x50.png 114w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-740x324.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Guarantee.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>The promise? If you decide Casper’s mattress isn’t for you, they’ll send a courier over to remove it from your home and either donate it to a local charity or have it recycled. Best of all, you don’t even need to have the box.<br></p>



<p>Casper isn’t just focused on making money; they’re interested in helping those in need and doing their part for the environment. This resonates with millennials, especially, who consider charity and the environment key deciding factors in their purchasing decisions. (ht: Rikke.)<br></p>



<p>There’s also a secondary benefit to offering a 100-night free-trial. Casper knows that once a customer makes the product a part of their everyday life, whether they know it or not, they’re far less likely to return it.<br></p>



<p>As mentioned above, Casper’s 100-night free trial isn’t something casually mentioned as an afterthought (such as on their checkout page). Rather, it’s something that’s consistent through each stage of their funnel (especially in their cart recovery emails which we’ll discuss in Part 5: Strategy#1).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: You probably already have a guarantee for your products. But is it unbeatable? Is it one that your customers love you for (and your competitors hate you for)? If not, consider lowering the barrier to entry so that your offer is too good for prospects to ignore.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>





<h2><strong>Part 2: Content Marketing</strong></h2>



<p>Casper leverage three content archetypes as part of their strategy, each with the goal of nudging prospects further along the purchase funnel.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>As a refresher, here’s an example of a funnel, including examples of content archetypes at each stage:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="470" height="421" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel.png" alt="Purchase Funnel" class="wp-image-86174" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel.png 470w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-300x269.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-380x340.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-56x50.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-220x197.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Purchase-Funnel-385x345.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-text-align-center"><em>Source: <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="http://cartina.se/guide-hur-jobba-med-content-marketing-har-ar-allt-du-behover-veta/tofu-mofu-bofu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Cartina</a></em></p>





<p>Let’s take a look.<br></p>





<h2 id="3"><strong>Strategy #3: Answer Your Target Market’s Questions (To-Fu)</strong></h2>



<p>Casper’s blog, <a href="http://blog.casper.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Pillow Talk</a>, ranks on page one for many medium-tail keywords such as “can’t sleep” and “sleeping positions.” They also rank for more general, long-tail search queries like “what to do when you can&#8217;t sleep” and “how to go to sleep earlier.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png" alt="Casper_s Organic Keywords" class="wp-image-86090" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-768x328.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-380x162.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-600x256.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-760x324.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-960x410.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-740x316.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-385x164.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Organic-Keywords.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Much of their To-Fu content is short-form and humorous, whereas others, as we’ll see in Part 3: Strategy #2, is well-researched.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="214" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png" alt="Casper Content Example" class="wp-image-85966" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-300x63.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-768x160.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-1536x320.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-380x79.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-600x125.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-760x159.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-1440x300.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-168x35.png 168w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-240x50.png 240w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-740x154.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example-385x80.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Content-Example.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Interestingly, rather than ask for an email address on these pages, Casper incentivize you to submit a survey about your sleeping habits, offering a $25 discount as a reward.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png" alt="Casper Survey Popup" class="wp-image-86018" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Survey-Popup.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, they ask questions about your preferred sleeping position, your evening routine, as well as general demographic questions about your age, income, gender, and more:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png" alt="Preferred Sleeping Position" class="wp-image-86166" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Preferred-Sleeping-Position.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>At the end of the survey, they ask for your email, before offering you a coupon code.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png" alt="Casper_s Survey Confirmation Page" class="wp-image-86126" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper even tracks how many visitors click “Shop Casper” after completing the survey to determine whether it’s a strategy worth continuing:<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="27" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png" alt="Promo Code Labs" class="wp-image-86170" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-768x20.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-1536x41.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-600x16.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-760x20.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-1440x38.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs-385x10.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Promo-Code-Labs.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And it’s clever, for three reasons:<br></p>



<ol><li>Answering their target buyer’s most pressing questions increases Casper’s organic footprint in the SERPs and positions them as a market authority.</li><li>Surveying visitors that have come from specific search queries gives them a highly-targeted focus group and feedback so they can improve their marketing.</li><li>Offering a discount, front-end, to a visitor who came from organic search fast-tracks impulse buyers without the need to pay for traffic (more on that in Part 4).&nbsp;</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Using sites like Quora and Reddit, research your target market’s most pressing questions and create content that answers those questions. To learn more about how to do that, step-by-step, <a aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">read this article</a>.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="4"><strong>Strategy #4: Create a Go-To Comparison Resource (MoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>A common obstacle to buying something, like a mattress, is not knowing which is right for you.<br></p>



<p>As mentioned above, there are lots of considerations such as the type of mattress, its size, its firmness, and more.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Casper help potential buyers overcome confusion with their <a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/mattress-size-comparison-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">mattress size comparison guide</a>.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png" alt="Casper_s Mattress Comparison Guide" class="wp-image-86078" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it isn’t very long, it does rank for hundreds of keywords in position #1, including several long-tail keywords like “king size bed dimensions” and “queen mattress dimensions.”&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="374" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png" alt="Casper_s Positions in The SERPs" class="wp-image-86098" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-768x281.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-600x219.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-760x278.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-96x35.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-137x50.png 137w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-220x80.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And, for keywords that it doesn’t rank position #1 for, it ranks for featured snippets (also known as Position #0).&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>For example, for “queen size bed dimensions in feet,” they rank position #6 (at time of writing), but rank for a featured snippet, stealing <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/find-featured-snippets/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">8.6% of all clicks</a> in the process.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="623" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png" alt="Queen Size Bed Dimensions in Feet" class="wp-image-86178" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-300x183.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-768x467.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-380x231.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-600x365.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-760x462.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-82x50.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-740x450.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-220x134.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-385x234.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>What’s interesting is, rather than ask you for feedback on this page, as they do for their To-Fu content, Casper invite you to enter a competition.&nbsp;</p>


