<p>It’s clever. A visitor who is comparing mattress sizes is likely further along the buyer’s journey than someone who is searching for sleeping aids. So, Casper asks for an email, rather than feedback, and introduce their products in their onboarding emails (more on that in Part 5).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: If you sell different types of product (e.g. cosmetics like foundation), create a comparison guide that helps buyers find the right one for them. Bonus if you can rank it well in the SERPs.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="5"><strong>Strategy #5: Showcase All Reviews in One Place (BoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>You know the importance of using customer testimonials to help close potential buyers. But are you showcasing them as best as you can?<br></p>



<p>Knowing the importance of reviews in a competitive market, Casper showcases all their reviews on one page on their site.<br></p>



<p>First, they feature written reviews by their customers, including the person’s name, where they’re from, and how they rate Casper.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png" alt="Casper_s Reviews" class="wp-image-86118" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-768x399.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-380x198.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-600x312.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-760x395.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-740x385.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Reviews.png 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Casper is 100% transparent here. If you click, “See all reviews,” you can read everything their customers say about them, including the unhappy ones.)<br></p>



<p>Beneath their customer reviews, you can read tweets from customers, adding further to the legitimacy of their reviews.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="393" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png" alt="Casper Tweet Testimonial" class="wp-image-86022" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-300x115.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-768x294.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-380x146.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-600x230.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-760x291.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-740x284.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-385x148.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Tweet-Testimonial.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Finally, Casper adds the third layering of social proof: media badges and press mentions.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png" alt="Casper_s Media Mentions" class="wp-image-86082" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-300x189.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-768x485.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1536x969.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-600x379.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-760x479.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1440x909.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-740x467.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions-385x243.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Media-Mentions.png 1585w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>There’s a reason why Casper go to such great lengths to optimize their review page and we’ll discuss why in Part 5: Strategy #2.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: It’s common for online stores to have their reviews on third-party sites. But that doesn’t always mean its a best practice. Take your best reviews and have them on one page on your site so you have more control over how you market your business.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>




