<h2><strong>Part 3: Link Building</strong></h2>



<p>As of writing, Casper has 148k backlinks from 5.54 referring domains.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png" alt="Casper_s Backlinks" class="wp-image-86030" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-1536x227.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-1440x213.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Backlinks.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>It’s impressive, but unless you have a multi-million dollar marketing budget, few of their link building strategies are replicable (if you’re curious, I’ve included my three favorites in the bonus resource).<br></p>



<p>So, rather than explore the unreplicable, I want to show you three unconventional ways Casper build links and how you can, too.&nbsp;<br></p>





<h2 id="6"><strong>Strategy #6: Build White-Hat Education Links with “The CSD Method”</strong></h2>



<p>If you know anything about link building, you know getting .edu links are the best you can get. They pass a TON of Page Rank, but they’re also tough to acquire. Unless, of course, you have a unique angle&#8230;<br></p>



<p>Take a look at Casper’s referring domains.<br></p>



<p>If we refine the search, we can see they’ve built twelve do-follow .edu links using, what I call, the college student discount (CSD) strategy.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png" alt="Education Links to Casper" class="wp-image-86134" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-1536x804.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-1440x754.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-740x388.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Education-Links-to-Casper.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, what is Casper doing to build these links?&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>They’re inserting their product into the lives of a market that may benefit from it:<br></p>



<p><em>Students.</em><br></p>



<p>Take a look at this page from California State University, Northridge (CSUN):<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png" alt="Link from CSUN" class="wp-image-86154" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-CSUN.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>On it, students can get discounts from a range of products and services including apparel, insurance—and mattresses.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="149" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png" alt="Casper Discount Code" class="wp-image-85974" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-1024x149.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-768x112.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-1536x223.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-380x55.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-600x87.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-760x111.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-1440x209.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-180x26.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-250x36.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-740x108.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-220x32.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-385x56.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code.png 1650w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Coincidence? Maybe. But probably not.<br></p>



<p>Here’s another example from The State University of New York, again, with a page discounting products and services for students.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png" alt="Link from SUNY" class="wp-image-86158" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-SUNY.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you scroll down, they, too, have a discount on any Casper mattress.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="274" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png" alt="Casper Discount Code 2" class="wp-image-85970" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-768x205.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-1536x410.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-380x102.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-600x160.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-760x203.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-1440x385.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-131x35.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-187x50.png 187w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-740x198.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-220x59.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2-385x103.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Discount-Code-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s impossible to know if Casper actively sought out these links and others, it’s highly likely, given the frequency of these type of links—and the PageRank they pass.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: It’s easy to assume building links like the above is impossible. But many sites, like CSUN, have a form where you can submit discounts of your own. Ask yourself, “Who else can I serve?” Then, consider where that target market hangs out and reach out to the right sites.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="7"><strong>Strategy #7: Publish Original Research (and Become a Go-To Expert in Your Marketplace)</strong></h2>



<p>In Section #2, we discussed the three content archetypes Casper use to generate search traffic. You also learned one of those archetypes was content that answers your target market’s questions.<br></p>



<p>Casper does a fine job of doing that. But, sometimes, answering a question goes beyond giving an opinion. In truth, to become an authority on a subject, you often need to cite, or even better, publish <em>original</em> research.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Take, for instance, Casper’s post, “<a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/faqs/ca-the-mattress/how-often-should-i-replace-my-mattress/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">How Often Should I Replace My Mattress?</a>”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png" alt="How Often Should I Replace My Mattress" class="wp-image-86146" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In it, Casper debunks an industry myth about how often you should change your mattress.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Rather than cite other people’s research, they use their own findings having researched their own mattresses, and set the record straight.<br></p>



<p>This page on their FAQ got a nice DR90 link from <a href="https://www.healthline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Healthline</a> which just goes to show:&nbsp;<br></p>



<p><em>Content doesn’t always have to be published on a blog for it to acquire links.</em>&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: If you’re creating content for your site, consider publishing original research (even if it’s a meta-analysis of other studies) Yes, it takes time. But it can also be an asset for sites in your marketplace to link to.</p>
</div></div>





<h2 id="8"><strong>Strategy #8: Use “The Best-of Backlink Builder” (with a Twist)</strong></h2>



<p>One of the quickest and easiest ways for online retailers to build links is to get featured in best-of content—content that curates the best of the best for a niche. (I call it “<a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">the best-of backlink builder</a>”).<br></p>



<p>For example, Casper has built several high domain authority links by getting featured in “best [keyword] ideas” content, such as “best wedding gift ideas.”<br></p>



<p>In fact, Casper has acquired several do-follow links from several high-authority sites like <a href="https://www.theknot.com/content/top-40-registry-picks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">The Knot</a> (DR:90) and <a href="https://www.brides.com/story/wedding-registry-splurges-and-group-gifts" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Brides</a> (DR:82) using this very strategy.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="230" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png" alt="Link from Brides" class="wp-image-86150" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-768x173.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-1536x346.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-600x135.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-760x171.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-1440x324.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-156x35.png 156w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-222x50.png 222w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-740x167.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides-385x87.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Link-from-Brides.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Now, here’s where it takes an interesting turn.<br></p>



<p><a href="https://heavy.com/social/2016/03/top-best-bridal-shower-gift-ideas-gifts-wedding-bride-unique/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">Heavy</a>, a news and information site, also feature Casper in a best-of article for “top bridal shower gift ideas.”<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png" alt="Top Bridal Shower Gift Ideas" class="wp-image-86186" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1536x749.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-600x293.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-760x371.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But upon closer inspection, it’s actually an affiliate link.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="25" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png" alt="Heavy Affiliate Link" class="wp-image-86138" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-300x7.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-768x19.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-380x9.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-600x15.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-760x19.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1440x35.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-180x4.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-250x6.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-740x18.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-220x5.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link-385x9.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Heavy-Affiliate-Link.png 1475w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>While it’s highly unlikely a site like Casper reached out to get featured in an article like this, it is likely sites like Heavy are more willing to link to a product if there’s a chance to earn a commission on the backend. (So, if you don’t have an affiliate program for your products, it might be worth thinking about.)<br></p>



<p>The best part about getting featured in best-of content, of course, is it’s scalable.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>Using a tool like Ahrefs, you can enter a competitor’s domain, click “Referring Domains &gt; Backlinks” to view the type of content they’re featured in. Then, you can go after similar sites. (To learn more about how to do a competitive analysis, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/competitive-analysis" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">read this in-depth guide</a>.)&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: The Best-Of Backlink Builder is a killer strategy if you sell products that are good gift ideas. Using search operators like “best [keyword] gifts” and “[keyword] gifts for [gender],” identify sites that could include your offer. Then, reach out to them. Yes, it’s time-consuming. But it’s a great e-commerce link building strategy.</p>
</div></div>





<h2><strong>Part 4: Paid Acquisition&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Like many multi-million dollar companies, Casper invests a fortune in paid advertising.<br></p>



<p>In fact, as of writing, their estimated monthly budget for Google Adwords, alone, is $128,000. (Source: <a href="https://www.similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SimilarWeb</a>).<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="398" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png" alt="Casper_s Paid Search" class="wp-image-86094" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-300x117.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-768x299.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-1536x597.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-380x148.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-600x233.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-760x295.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-1440x560.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-129x50.png 129w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-740x288.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-220x86.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search-385x150.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Paid-Search.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>But that doesn’t mean their strategies can’t be modelled on a smaller scale.<br></p>



<p>Here are my three favorite strategies I found while researching.<br></p>





<h2 id="9"><strong>Strategy #9: Translate Your Ads to Capture New Markets</strong></h2>



<p>A good marketer knows which countries are driving the most traffic to their site.<br></p>



<p>Casper is no exception.<br></p>



<p>Using a tool like <a href="http://similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">SimilarWeb</a>, we can see the majority of Casper’s traffic comes from the United States, the United Kingdom, Canada, France, and Germany.&nbsp;<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="493" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png" alt="Casper_s Traffic by Countries" class="wp-image-86130" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-768x370.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1536x739.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-600x289.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-760x366.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1440x693.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>So, it makes sense that Casper advertises to users in the United States, the United Kingdom, and Canada in English. After all, for the US and the UK, (and 56.9% of Canada), English is the mother tongue.&nbsp;<br></p>



<p>But what about countries like France and Germany where English isn’t the first language?<br></p>



<p>Casper is growing their market share in other countries by translating their ads into the target country&#8217;s first language.<br></p>



<p>Take, for instance, the following display ad, shown to German visitors who have previously visited Casper’s site.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="728" height="90" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png" alt="Casper_s German Display Ad" class="wp-image-86050" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png 728w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-300x37.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-380x47.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-600x74.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-250x31.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-385x48.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></figure></div>



<p>When clicked, users are taken to a landing page with German copy and customer support.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png" alt="Casper_s German Landing Page" class="wp-image-86058" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Landing-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>If you try to leave, Casper shows a <a href="https://sleeknote.com/collect-email-addresses?ref=casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" aria-label=" (opens in a new tab)">exit-intent popup</a> asking for your email address.<br></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="767" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png" alt="Casper_s German Exit Intent Popup" class="wp-image-86054" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-300x225.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-768x575.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-380x285.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-600x449.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-760x569.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1440x1079.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-654x490.png 654w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-220x165.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-385x288.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup.png 1455w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>In English it reads:<br></p>



<p>“We will soon make one of your dreams come true. Sign up and never ‘sleep over’ from news, products and discounts from Casper.”<br></p>



<p>This strategy works well for three reasons:<br></p>



<ol><li>Translating ad copy into a target market’s language personalizes your marketing.&nbsp;</li><li>Offering customer support helps readers overcome objections to buying (more on that in Strategy #12).</li><li>Capturing abandoning visitors’ email addresses gives you an opportunity to remarket using another media (like email).&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Action Item</strong>: Log into Google Analytics and click, “Audience &gt; Overview &gt; Country” to identify your audience by country. Then, consider translating your ad copy into the mother tongue of one or more of those countries.</p>
</div></div>




